frames.caption: A futuristic blue sports car with sleek, aerodynamic design speeds along a coastal road. The car's unique wing-like doors are raised, adding to its striking appearance. The background features a scenic ocean view with cliffs and trees lining the road.
frames.description: The scene captures a high-tech sports car driving on a winding coastal road. The setting is serene with the ocean on one side and cliffs with trees on the other, suggesting a blend of technology and nature.

frames.caption: A towering robot stands majestically on a rooftop, overlooking a cityscape. The sky is filled with dramatic clouds, enhancing the imposing presence of the robot.
